<c74object name="CH-Timer">

	<digest>
		Timer Module for Collab-Hub.
	</digest>
	
	<description>
Coordinate time between users in performance. The CH-Timer module allows users to synchronize time-based events across all connected clients. This is useful for collaborative performances where timing is critical.
	This module uses the jweb object to display a timer interface within Max. Users can start, stop, and reset the timer, and the current time will be broadcast to all connected clients.
	This is running an instance of the CH-Timer web app hosted on Collab-Hub servers at https://server.collab-hub.io/timer.html.
	</description>
	
